    <briefdescription>
<para>Base class for collecting validation errors in builder patterns. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class provides error accumulation functionality for builders that cannot throw exceptions. Builder methods can call <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1ErrorCollector_1abed0ef518f8268eb832b24ea41a11733" kindref="member">AddError()</ref> to accumulate validation errors, and <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1ErrorCollector_1a16cbe7b6d423a372c9e68d970ff2c3ea" kindref="member">CheckErrors()</ref> returns all errors at once.</para>
<para>Example usage: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="keyword">class<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">MyBuilder<sp/>:<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">public</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>ErrorCollectorBase<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">public</highlight><highlight class="normal">:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>MyBuilder&amp;<sp/>SetValue(</highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>val)<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">if</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>(val<sp/>&lt;<sp/>0)<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">return</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>AddError(ErrorKind::kInvalidArgument,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;Value<sp/>must<sp/>be<sp/>non-negative&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>value_<sp/>=<sp/>val;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">return</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>*</highlight><highlight class="keyword">this</highlight><highlight class="normal">;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>Result&lt;MyObject&gt;<sp/>Build()<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>ICEBERG_RETURN_UNEXPECTED(CheckErrors());</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">return</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>MyObject{value_};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">private</highlight><highlight class="normal">:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>value_<sp/>=<sp/>0;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
